OL,11,Fevidence presented by Sir Simon        
OL,12,FStevens, the former NHS England chief. 
OL,14,FIn his witness statement, he said Mr   
OL,15,FHancock thought he, not doctors or the 
OL,16,Fpublic, should decide who to prioritise
OL,17,Fif hospitals became overwhelmed.       
